 becoming a professor by steven m cahn covers an extensive range of critical issues from dissertation to tenure useful for beginning graduate study working to secure an academic position or striving to build a professorial career paths to the professoriate strategies for enriching the preparation of future faculty by donald wulff ann e austin & associates brings together major research the most important developments in practice and informed analysis on preparing future faculty the academic marathon managing the academic career by shelley taylor and joanne martin compilation of articles regarding academic careers tomorrow's professor preparing for academic careers in science and engineering by richard reis resource for science and engineering academic careers offers a practical approach to career development online resources the chronicle of higher education articles and advice about academic careers and the academic job search successful academic resources and tips for finishing your dissertation landing a faculty position and obtaining tenure preparing future faculty resources for future faculty back to top career paths for phd students up careers outside academia groups career development center printer friendly version calendar schedule an appointment graphic calendar pages schedule an appointment with a career counselor quick links calendar career fair schedule career planning handbook career library vault guided career path facebook linkedin what is the cdc copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
